        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">If you stand during the whole fight clicking your bone ring of condemnation, though it is not costing you manna, you are losing the manna you would gain from medding, as there is an opportunity cost involved.  For 6 applications of the ring, that is 250 manna for a 60th level necro.  (6 applications times 10 seconds divided by 6 seconds times 25 manna per tick) And you just did 450 damage for 250 manna.  Is that efficient damage?  It is more efficient damage than our taps, but less efficient than our higher level DD's, DOT's or Vex/BoD.  </P><P>But it sounds like you are having fun and that is really what it is all about.  I enjoy mixing things up and doing things in odd ways to add flavor sometimes.</P><P>Ishtarra Gemeinseele<BR>Warlock of Tunare</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
