        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">If I lost all my gear permanently and had to choose 3 right click items, my first choice would be my pre-nerf circlet. Probably Jboots next (of course with the next running skill in Luclin this might quickly be erased from this list). Since they are just plain sexy, Holgresh Elder Beads would get my last vote. </P><P>When I first read about the right click ring I was not all that excited, but after reading these posts and pondering it a bit more, I am really getting excited about it. </P><P>As far as Luclin goes, there are 2 right clickers on my drool list. Coterie Mask of the Dead (right click for FD with a 0.0 recast time) and Orb of the Lost Souls (right click for +3HP, +3Mana per tick for 45 minutes as well as a 150HP damage skin). </P><P>Through it all, even if I could chose among the items I did not have, my top pick would still be, and will always likely be my pre-nerfed circlet. Handy almost everywhere and for the truly enlightened among us, an item of untold power. </P><P>Cheers,<BR>Ancagalon the Black</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
