        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">First, let me share my views concerning the Bone Ring:</P><P>10sec...75<BR>20sec...150<BR>30sec...225<BR>40sec...300. --> Standing for 40 sec to get a manafree Deflux, but you dont get the bonus of mana you get from siting down to med. I'm not finding it too good.. Also, if you solo with pet tanking and do only 450 damage per minute, youre pet will outdamage you..less xp.</P><P>I personally only used the ring sometimes after a CR to recover faster but that is rare, most of the time there is a healer around with free mana to heal ya. The caster time is huge and 75hp is quite low for a lvl 60 :(</P><P>---</P><P>My most used right click items are, indeed, CoS, epic, bracer. I dont use JBoots anymore. My favorite gotta be CoS cause it has many use to save your ass. Then I'd say Epic followed very close by Bracer.</P><P>GOTTA GET VP STAFF!</P><P>Spherik Darksavant, Warlock</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
